_sText:
Another Jailbreak map i've done.

It's set in old times as you can tell, And it contains hanging area (Prefab), Trap door, Gates and more.

Players spawn inside dungeons.

Some people on my server dislike it, Some like it. It's a like or hate sort of map.

I'm unable to find the authors of the prefabs right now, But contact me if you're a author for credit.

I got the basic idea of a Fight yard map, Although i did do this map from scratch.
